#: ../../manual/rigging/constraints/tracking/track_to.rst:43
msgid "Follow Bendy Bones"
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/rigging/constraints/tracking/track_to.rst:43
msgid ""
"When using a b-bone as a target, click on this button to make the target "
"point between head and tail follow the length of the B-Spline curve "
"instead of the absolute distance of the head and tail of the original "
"b-bone."
msgstr ""

